<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;">Putman 9</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 8pt;"> – USAF Major, operations officer, 328th Weapons Squadron, United States Air Force Weapons School, former chief,</span>
